data.description: Welcome to this fantastic, stately 3 side brick home in highly sought after Echo Mill! 2 story entry foyer welcomes you inside & opens to formal dining room on the right-straight ahead leads into the large family room offering plenty of natural light & fireplace to anchor the room. Kitchen features white cabinets with adjoining breakfast area leading to a screened porch/deck that's perfect for enjoying morning coffee & peaceful quiet Fall evenings. Hardwoods in foyer, family/dining rooms. Owners retreat is located on the main level w/adjoining ensuite, his/her walk-in closets. Downstairs has two additional rooms that are being used as teen bedroom w/full bath & home office/craft room. 3 car garage with exterior basement entrance making for perfect inlaw suite. Fenced backyard on one of the larger lots in the neighborhood & adjoins to vacant wooded lot that features a quaint park-like setting. Echo Mill offers wonderful amenities including pools, tennis, walking trails, playground, sidewalks, fishing pond & clubhouses. Outstanding schools, wonderful West Cobb location which is close to dining, shopping etc.
